others are not fully informed you can help to communicate the needs of stanford law school as well as keep your classmates up to date on the latest stanford law school news how it works the stanford law school reunion staff recruits a reunion team that consists of a chair and a committee of 10 to 15 individuals though there is no limit to the number of committee members there is not a minimum gift requirement but members are encouraged to make personally significant commitments each volunteer agrees to call several classmates to encourage a participatory gift and attendance at the reunion find out about additional volunteer opportunities at the law school reuinions will be here related links online alumni directory giving to the law school giving to stanford cloudy 50 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
